_sText:
Hey! This is my first map I've ever made and I worked hard on it. I designed it for sniper and ground battles, since I like both, and I added some neat lighting to make it feel like it's morning. No music/ambient sounds yet, but I might include that in V2. if anyone can show me how, please PM me. Also thanks to 3kliksphilip for his awesome tutorial to help me make my first map.

KNOWN BUGS:

-Some parts of the map are messed up/floating (will fix)
-Bots commit suicide a lot (will try to fix)
-Ladder's width is too much (easy to fix)

Constructive critism is welcomed
